com.siperian.sif.message

Class HubStateIndicator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.HubStateIndicator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable

    public class HubStateIndicator
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable
    This class encapsulates the HUB_STATE_IND column and its possible values. This is used to represent the possible system states in the Hub.
